      <title>梅斯特稱聯準會將在某個時候降息，但不著急</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/fed-cut-us-rates-at-some-point-no-hurry-mester-says-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克利夫蘭聯邦儲備銀行行長洛雷塔·梅斯特週三表示，她預計今年物價壓力將進一步緩解，從而使聯準會能夠降低借貸成本，但前提是聯準會「相當有信心」通膨持續向2%的目標邁進。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/fed-cut-us-rates-at-some-point-no-hurry-mester-says-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 23:06:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
